headline: Teledyne to Participate at the TD Cowen Aerospace & Defense Conference
summary: THOUSAND OAKS, Calif., February 11, 2026--Teledyne Technologies Incorporated (NYSE:TDY) today announced that George Bobb, President and Chief Executive Officer, and Jason VanWees, Vice Chairman, will present at the TD Cowen 47th Annual Aerospace & Defense Conference at the Ritz-Carlton – Pentagon City in Arlington, Virginia on Thursday, February 12, at 11:30 a.m. Eastern Time.

headline: 2 Industrials Stocks for Long-Term Investors and 1 We Turn Down
summary: Whether you see them or not, industrials businesses play a crucial part in our daily activities. They are also bound to benefit from a friendlier regulatory environment with the Trump administration, and this excitement has led to a six-month gain of 27% for the sector - higher than the S&P 500’s 9.1% return.
